name: Useful Javascript Library
tagline: Useful set of tools to automate the creating of things using JavaScript Objects
body:

2. BreadCrumb Creator
3. Simple HTML AJAX
4. Radio Button Value To DOM

6. Grab and Serialize Form Data
7. Ajax Send w/ Modal Popup

9. Dropdown Sub Menu Height
10. Equal Height of child divs
11. IE Image Replace
